        " سمعته يقول: ينبغي للرجل إذا أصبح ان يقرأ بعد التعقيب خمسين آية"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "[2/1552] al-Tahdhib: Muhammad b. Ahmad b. Yahya from Muawiya b. Hukaym from Mu’ammar b. Khallad from al-Ridha عليه السلام. He (Mu’ammar) said: I heard him (i.e. the Imam) saying: It is incumbent on a man when he wakes up (in the morning) that he recite after the Taʿqīb (post dawn-prayer supplications) fifty verses"
        ]
      }
